These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
Job: pilot, accountant, writer, journalist
1. Beverage:lemonade is somewhere to the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##5
2. Job:journalist is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3
3. Job:pilot is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:water is somewhere to the left of Job:journalist##5
5. Job:pilot == Beverage:lemonade##1
6. Beverage:sprite == Job:accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Job   | writer | journalist      | pilot | accountant |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
Game: scrabble, chess, mah-jongg, whist
Pet: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. Game:chess is between Pet:bird and Pet:horse##2
2. Game:whist is somewhere to the left of Pet:horse##5
3. Pet:bird is on the right of Pet:goat##1
4. Pet:bird is on the right of Game:whist##1
5. Pet:chinchilla is on the left of Game:scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg | chess   | scrabble |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

