.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
Food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
House: cape-cod, colonial, craftsman, cottage
1. Food:corn == House:colonial##1
2. House:cottage is on the right of Food:corn##1
3. House:craftsman is somewhere to the left of House:cape-cod##5
4. House:cape-cod is on the left or right of Food:peach##3
5. Food:potato is somewhere to the right of House:cottage##5
6. Food:corn is somewhere to the left of House:craftsman##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| House   | colonial  | cottage   | craftsman | cape-cod    |

