.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
Hobby: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
Music-Genre: house, soul, funk, pop
1. Hobby:card-games is on the left of Hobby:singing##1
2. Hobby:woodworking is somewhere to the right of Music-Genre:funk##5
3. Hobby:card-games is between Music-Genre:pop and Music-Genre:soul##2
4. Music-Genre:funk is on the left or right of Music-Genre:pop##3
5. Music-Genre:pop == Hobby:skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | funk     | soul    | house       |

